title: Жуки
overview: Nikita, Dan and Artemy have developed a unique app for smartphones, they are about to sell it and make all their dreams come true. But at the last moment, the multi-million dollar deal breaks down and the guys are taken into the army. In order not to jeopardize the success of their startup, they choose an alternative service in the remote village of Zhuki, where they will try to complete their project. But it's not so easy to develop an application where there is not even the Internet ...
